cp|8|AT|^B@2^Z@3^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|The auction was good. With a nice 6 card heart suit and a singleton spade, 4H is clear. Now, having said that, you should strain to bid 4S over 4H, using the law of total tricks as your guide.With a singleton spade and 3 hearts, I cannot bid 4S, but it does bother me. Basically, 4S as a sacrifice over 4H is often a good result, so you should do so if there is any excues. However, I cannot justify it on this hand.|
